title: Wannihorn
text: The Wannihorn is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> of the <a href="Bernese%20Alps">Bernese Alps</a>, located north of <a href="Hohtenn">Hohtenn</a> in the canton of <a href="Valais">Valais</a>. It lies south of the <a href="Wilerhorn%20%28Bernese%20Alps%29">Wilerhorn</a>, on the range between the lower <a href="L%C3%B6tschental">Lötschental</a> and the Jolital.
